Text: RE Delphi ISDA Worksheet Cc Stephanie I would need the ISDA to be sent tomorrow Can you get it to me I need to send it with an accompanying letter Thanks ext ES Original Message From Phillips Rebecca Sent Thursday October PM To Panus Stephanie Cc Curry Ken Noel Thierry Subject Delphi ISDA Worksheet Attached is the ISDA worksheet for Delphi Automotive Systems Corp Please let me know if you need anything else r File Delphi ISDAxls

Delphi Automotive DPH Cc Stephanie I need to get an ISDA setup with Delphi Automotive NYSE DPH Ken Curry is looking into credit limits As soon as you have it ready thanks for forwarding to me the two copies I am now located in Enron South at I want to forward it with other documents to the client Many Thanks ext
